<span id="more-821"></span><br />
<a href="http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/cover2.png"><img src="http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/cover2.png" alt="" title="cover2" width="497" height="702" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-822" /></a></p>
